      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，IngressController 作为起点连到 Still。那 Still 这个状态后续有哪些分支？是只连 EtcdCluster，还是有其他去向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Still 要有两条线：一条指向 Infra_EtcdCluster，另一条指向一个叫 Moving 的运行状态。另外，Moving 和 Still 之间要能双向回退。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Still ↔ Moving 双向，Still → EtcdCluster。那 Moving 除了回退到 Still，还有别的出口吗？比如异常场景？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Moving 还要能进入 Crash 状态，表示服务崩溃。而且 Crash 之后不能直接恢复，必须先落到 EtcdCluster 做一致性检查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：Moving → Crash，以及 Crash → EtcdCluster。我检查一下整体结构：IngressController 起始于 Still，Still 分叉到 EtcdCluster 和 Moving，Moving 可回退 Still 或进入 Crash，Crash 最终落到 EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Crash 到 EtcdCluster 的箭头方向好像画反了？应该是 Crash 指向 EtcdCluster，表示崩溃后由 EtcdCluster 接管，不是反过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Crash → EtcdCluster 是从 Crash 指向 EtcdCluster，表示崩溃后流转到 EtcdCluster 做恢复。这个方向是对的，没有反。",
      "elements_involved": [
